{"tid":1302237,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［發夢發大達］每日打電話去TVB新聞部，直播問股價","createTime":"2019-07-10T01:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T04:17:25.000Z","uid":251949,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e406d9f572967c59220c76e4ff3bace7d53bc256","tid":1302237,"uid":251949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:27:53.000Z","msg":"早幾日發夢，大家每日問股炒股發大財<br />\n<br />\n年輕人想學買股票，每日了解股票走勢，或者即場打電話問股價，<br />\n一定要睇無綫財經資訊台嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />＂智富360＂<br />\n嘉賓大多數都係來自早前發聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />譴責「暴徒」嘅＂香港股票分析師協會＂成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190709/59806488\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190709%2F59806488&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8Cl6E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=90612d02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190709%2F59806488&h=da15a31d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190709/59806488</a><br />\n逢港股交易日，一至五現場直播。<br />\n<br />\n家庭觀眾問股登記流程：<br />\n１）打電話，幕後編輯預先登記：股票，幾時買／應否持貨／留電話同貴姓<br />\n２）節目直播前，幕後會隨機揀選電話(問大路股票較為被選中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，打返界觀眾準備直播提問<br />\n３）直播時，主拎TAG觀眾出場，觀眾約有１０秒自行發問（記得把握時間問問題），之後就會ＣＵＴ電話聲<br />\n４）聆聽分析師謂解股價走勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新聞部主要贊助收入來源：<br />\n１）地產代理特約贊助（大客：中原／利嘉閤）<br />\n２）窩輪商（瑞銀／摩根大通／中銀）<br />\n主持 :蔡康年（另一身份：香港股票分析師協會會員）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6gTxKW7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6gTxKW7.jpg&h=f1d73f95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n３）地產商／金融機構（新鴻基信貸／大新金融／<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />資本策略（同陳國強非常老友））"},{"pid":"89c751a7df436799545317f413ad9f6f5a180562","tid":1302237,"uid":251949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:04:27.000Z","msg":"聽講tvb廣告收入多少,<br />\n對新聞部影響唔算直接。<br />\n<br />\n直接斷佢水喉, 可能仲有效果"},{"pid":"6237f698588b3856bd7bf1a616d633a9ecf37ae1","tid":1302237,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2d9d39c0b8c31b55d9f6d0425fd4d8118a5bdc","tid":1302237,"uid":144739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:05:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"119d04ab64038e3aa12d684f9594de860337d55b","tid":1302237,"uid":153824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:12:07.000Z","msg":"問返TVB股價<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8a93e30f16ecc54189c28193e00964673a1834","tid":1302237,"uid":251949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:12:08.000Z","msg":"溫提:<br />\n到時問咩都好, 記得把握時間, <br />\n離題會被cut線"},{"pid":"fd310f666ad18063e513ffb798dce56f1aa813a1","tid":1302237,"uid":251949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"119d04ab64038e3aa12d684f9594de860337d55b","tid":1302237,"uid":153824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:12:07.000Z","msg":"問返TVB股價<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:12:58.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好問人地老細喺邊, 乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e2d6f852ee8578600fd05cae6b98123f3009e8","tid":1302237,"uid":101345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:16:08.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2f29d73688c0544004127656f9b1d17a3e1e1480","tid":1302237,"uid":209873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:18:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"359b1b6914af4a08cbbf0fe2a0c27e11b5b2f237","tid":1302237,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":